node.text: Are you team hot dog or team hamburger? We caught wind that you can have the best of both worlds with @rastellibutchers round hot dogs… so @annibell14 had to give them a try! 🌭🍔 Watch to find out if they’re worth it, and tap the blue link in our bio for where to find them. #allrecipes #hotdogs #hamburgers #grillingseason
